[[File:Taiteilijaseura NYTE 3h+k.jpg|thumb|NYTE's premises in center of [[Pori]].]]
'''Art Association NYTE [[rekisteröity yhdistys|ry]]''' is founded in 1987 in [[Pori]] as an artist group and art [[Voluntary association|association]]. It is as a launching platform for young [[artist]]s in Satakunta Region.<ref name="Website">[http://nyte.arkku.net/nyte.html Nyten esittely seuran kotisivuilla] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091112142405/http://nyte.arkku.net/nyte.html |date=November 12, 2009 }}</ref>

Art Association NYTE ry begun as an [[interdisciplinary]] artist group which included artists from various fields including, [[fine-art]], Cinema and [[Live art|Live-Arts]].

Many of NYTE's activities take place in the social centre 3h+k. Which translates as 3 rooms and a kitchen. It includes a theatre, gallery space and computer resource room. There is also an outside yard used for some performances and was started in the 1980s.

